# DeviceDrop

DeviceDrop simulates the frontend for an device renting service.

## Build with:

[![My Skills](https://skillicons.dev/icons?i=js,nextjs,react,tailwind,)](https://skillicons.dev) && framer-motion

## Demo

[.](https://devicedrop.vercel.app/)


## Features

- Framer Animations
- Responsive
- React-Countup
- Date Picker
